6e46b0ac35cc0.mp4?t=1746727942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Game Story:</strong><br>The game features an epic and immersive storyline. There are several bosses in the game that you need to reach by ascending the levels. Upon reaching the final level, you will engage in a battle with the boss.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821380/extras/4cc3ad67ef7b86dbcf273759628b2b65.poster.avif?t=1746727942\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821380/extras/4cc3ad67ef7b86dbcf273759628b2b65.webm?t=1746727942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821380/extras/4cc3ad67ef7b86dbcf273759628b2b65.mp4?t=1746727942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Cards:</strong><br>In the full version, there will be a total of 60 cards and enchantments that will be used for various purposes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821380/extras/5396386679b2441ad108edf126980917.poster.avif?t=1746727942\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821380/extras/5396386679b2441ad108edf126980917.webm?t=1746727942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821380/extras/5396386679b2441ad108edf126980917.mp4?t=1746727942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Game Difficulty :</strong><br>The game's difficulty curve changes with a different slope, providing users with a new experience with each continued play.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821380/extras/44c4a5df88226468940550977dabfac4.poster.avif?t=1746727942\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821380/extras/44c4a5df88226468940550977dabfac4.webm?t=1746727942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2821380/extras/44c4a5df88226468940550977dabfac4.mp4?t=1746727942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
